    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. It runs smooth and is ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
