    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that perfectly balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you will find the expected minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. All body panels are straight and free of significant dents. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is remarkably clean; the upholstery shows only light softening on the driver's side bolster, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the intuitive infotainment system\u2014operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a consistent service history that includes recent oil changes and a fresh set of all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining. The transmission shifts smoothly, and the engine provides responsive power without any hesitation. This is a reliable, turn-key car that offers a premium driving experience for the discerning buyer who values both aesthetic appeal and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
