    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun to drive? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own. She\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, regularly maintained, and ready to hit the road for many more adventures! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend getaway, this beauty won't let you down. Come take her for a spin and see for yourself!",
