    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound example of a driver-focused icon. This chassis remains remarkably composed, benefiting from a recent comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a valve clearance adjustment to ensure the high-revving naturally aspirated inline-six maintains its factory-spec power delivery. The 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement with no synchro grind, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that provides excellent mechanical grip through the apex. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the subframe has been inspected and reinforced, and the suspension geometry is dialed in with polyurethane bushings for enhanced steering feedback. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes driving dynamics and mechanical integrity.",
